13
Subtitle
14
15 TO CREATE THE ARKANSAS CHILDREN AND
16 TEENS' ONLINE PRIVACY PROTECTION ACT.
17
18 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
19
20 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 4, Chapter 88, is amended to add an
21 additional subchapter to read as follows:
22 Subchapter 15 — Arkansas Children and Teens' Online Privacy Protection Act
23
24 4-88-1501. Title.
25 This subchapter shall be known and may be cited as the "Arkansas
26 Children and Teens' Online Privacy Protection Act".
27
28 4-88-1502. Definitions.
29 As used in this subchapter:
30 (1) "Child" means an individual twelve (12) years of age or
31 younger in the State of Arkansas;
32 (2) "Connected device" means a device that is capable of
33 connecting to the Internet, directly or indirectly, or to another connected
34 device;
35 (3) "Consent" means any reasonable effort, taking into
36 consideration available technology and including without limitation a request
